  "texts": [
    "We also measured the recommended queries (i.e., suggestive links) that the participants with SUGGESTIVE ++ bot clicked as well as the queries that the participants filled in the chat box by themselves.",
    "We examined how many tokens (terms) are contained in the participants' reported opinions.",
    "In the study, we asked the participants to report their opinions with reasons without setting minimum requirements for opinion length.",
    "We assumed that the more persuasive opinions the participants were encouraged to write, the longer their opinions would be.",
    "Therefore, we calculated the token-based length of participant opinions using MeCab, a Japanese morphological analyzer."
  ],
